('0c97ac2e-528b-11', 'Social-Media-by-newsboxx.webp', 'Social-Media-by-newsboxx', 'Social-Media-by-newsboxx', 'TOP 5 Alternative For WHATSAPP Messenger', 'top-5-alternative-for-whatsapp-messenger', '\r\nAs WHATSAPP is one of the most used apps in INDIA, It is nearly used by every individual, People use the app for communication purpose and entertainment, People enjoy using <b>WhatsApp</b> but due to change in their <b>privacy policy</b>, There are many issues of security so many people might start using some other alternative of WHATSAPP here are the top 5 list.\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"img/home/Telegram-by-newsboxx.webp\" class=\"float-left\" width=\"380\" alt=\"Telegram-by-newsboxx\">\r\n<h3>1. TELEGRAM MESSENGER</h3>\r\nAs we know <b>TELEGRAM</b> is the best competitor for WHATSAPP in the field of <b>messengers</b>, TELEGRAM is widely used in <b>INDIA</b>, In the app, you can do normal <b>chatting</b> but you can also use some other feature mainly telegram is used to <b>download movies</b>, <b>web series</b> It also has a feature of creating a supergroup in which you can add 100,000 people and can make your channels it gives you the ability to share the huge files of 1.5GB, You can also add privacy to your chats with a passcode, The bots of the telegram are also very good they let you play the games inside the messaging app which is not seen in WhatsApp, It also has a very good <b>calling feature</b> which gives you <b>good quality of calls</b>, Nowadays it is available <b>Andriod</b>,<b> IOS</b>, <b>windows phone</b>,<b>macOS</b>, <b>Linux</b>,<b> web</b>, etc.\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"img/home/singnal-by-newsboxx.webp\" class=\"float-right\" width=\"380\" alt=\"singnal-by-newsboxx\">\r\n<h3>2. SIGNAL PRIVATE MESSENGER</h3>\r\n<b>SIGNAL MESSENGER</b> is a type of messenger which is a <b>mixture of WhatsApp and Facebook</b> it is having the features of both app <b>WhatsApp and Facebook</b>, Nowadays it is trending on the <b>app store on iPhone</b>, It is downloading on a wide scale as WhatsApp had made changes in their privacy policy, SIGNAL give you more features than WhatsApp and any other messenger, It offers you the feature of <b>self-destructing</b> messages screen security, no one can take <b>chats screenshots</b>, the signal also brings <b>encryption</b> to its <b>backups</b>,<b> calls</b>,<b> group calls</b>, and every <b>data</b> in the <b>app</b>. ALSO, the messages and files you share by using the signal messenger are safe with no chances of leaking the data, SIGNAL doesn\'t link any data to your identity it is available in both Andriod as well as IOS.\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"img/home/discord-by-newsboxx.webp\" class=\"float-left\" width=\"380\" alt=\"discord-by-newsboxx\">\r\n<h3>3. DISCORD</h3>\r\n<b>DISCORD</b> is the best messenger for <b>gamers</b> at first it was just used by gamers to <b>chat and talk</b> on <b>calls while playing games</b> but nowadays it is also used as WhatsApp, Now you can easily \r\nchat in private with good <b>secure messaging</b> now they had added many new <b>gifs, emotes, images, and even document</b>, The quality of calls is also very good it also has many small games which you can play with your <b>friends</b> while playing games, The quality of <b>video calling</b> is also good now can also do <b>group video calling</b> there are also giving the <b>feature of screen sharing</b>, which makes it a good platform for <b>game streaming</b>, People can also earn money by making use of discord by creating their servers, DISCORD has got all covered feature os WhatsApp and many other good features than Whatsapp it is available in both Andriod, IOS It is also available in <b>windows and mac</b>, You can create a group of calling of 10 peoples.\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"img/home/bridgefy-app-by-newsboxx.webp\" class=\"float-right\" width=\"380\" alt=\"bridgefy-app-by-newsboxx\">\r\n<h3>4. BRIDGEFY</h3>\r\n<B>BRIDGEFY</b> is one of the searched apps nowadays because it performs a platform to chat which you can use <b>without internet</b>, You can chat send messages to your friend while even you are offline, It works by creating a network by using <b>Bluetooth</b>,<b> WIFI</b> direct on which your mobile will allow you to send messages to your <b>nearby friends</b>, You can also send messages to the friend living far away from you by creating group this app is very useful as you can send messages offline without internet \r\nand these app is free so you can easily enjoy these messenger, In these messenger, you can send messages <b>person to person</b>, <b>broadcast mode</b> and <b>mesh mode</b>, It provides <b>strong security</b> as messaging is carried offline there is no much threat of <b>hacking or leaking data</b>, This app is available in both Andriod and IOS.\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"img/home/kik-app-by-newsboxx.webp\" class=\"float-left\" width=\"380\" alt=\"kik-app-by-newsboxx\">\r\n<h3>5. KIK</h3>\r\n<b>KIK</b> is an <b>awesome messaging app</b> to the people who don\'t want to make visible number to operate a <b>messaging application</b>, While the app like WHATSAPP and many other messengers require a <B>mobile number</b> to operate <b>chatting and messaging</b>, Many users do not feel comfortable to share their number to chat for a short time as their number get leaked and which make cause bullying by making calls to the users so these messengers provide you the platform to chat without entering your mobile numbering it operates by using <b>EMAIL ID</b>. Once you sign in KIK will create a new <b>username</b> Due to which there is no <b>leaking of your data</b>, As per these they provide <b>very strong security</b>, You will also get an <b>important feature</b> which is required while chatting such as <b>stickers, emojis, GIF, photo sharing</b> also video sharing you can <b>play quizzes, fashion tips and also latest news</b>, It is available in both Andriod and IOS.\r\n\r\n', 'Social Media', '5 Best Alternatives of WhatsApp, privacy policy, awesome messaging app, chatting and messaging, WhatsApp and Facebook', '2021-01-09', '2021-01-09 14:57:49', 'Pritesh', 68),
('11f01ba9-4e55-11', 'mini_Faug-by-newsboxx.webp', 'Faug-game', 'Faug-game', 'FAU-G GAME IS GOING TO LAUNCH SOON', 'fau-g-game-is-going-to-launch-soon', '<b>FAU-G</b> is an <b>INDIAN Game</b> made by <b>NCORE gaming company</b> situated at <b>BANGALORE</b>, This game is based on the INDIAN army, They are planning to launch these games on the following <b>republic day</b> which is on <b>26 January</b>.\r\n\r\nThe release date of the game was announced on 3 January, They had also launched one more theatrical trailer of their game on these days by showing the bravery of our <b>INDIAN soldiers</b> in the war of <b>Ladakh</b>, In which the INDIAN troops are fighting against PLA troops.\r\n\r\nThe first teaser of the FAU-G game was released on Dussehra 2020, In that teaser, they had shown the bravery of Indian soldiers in <b>Galwan Valley</b>, In the first teaser they had not shown any weapon, They had only shown combat, But in the new teaser which was launched on 3 January they had shown weapons and also combat these trailers give us a major hint of the game, We can also see the dialogues in the Punjabi language which makes the game awesome as we have Indian language in the game, It might get a very good result as it is on of awaited game in India, It will make the <b>Indian gaming industry</b> strong.', 'Esports', 'Fau-G Launch Soon', '2021-01-04', '2021-01-04 06:21:24', 'Paresh', 161),
('25c62ed3-54f5-11', 'Qualcomm-3d-senson-by-newsboxx.webp', 'Qualcomm-3d-senson-by-newsboxx', 'Qualcomm-3d-senson-by-newsboxx', 'Qualcomm Launch New 3D Sonic 2nd Gen Fingerprint Sensor', 'qualcomm-launch-new-3d-sonic-2nd-gen-fingerprint-sensor', '\r\nToday Qualcomm is reporting the arrival of their new second era <b><i>ultrasonic fingerprint sensor</i></b>. Yet, Qualcomm\'s trying once more. The organization on Tuesday at its third yearly Snapdragon Innovation Culmination presented its new unique sensor, the 3D Sonic Max. The greatest change in this new sensor is its size, it\'s bigger.\r\n\r\nBack in 2019, the organization had delivered its first-generation sensor, generally outstanding for being utilized in <b><i>Samsung\'s Galaxy S10 and S20</i></b> arrangement of gadgets, offering another option and altogether different innovation contrasted with the competition optical-based unique sensor arrangements.<br>\r\n<img src=\"img/home/qualcomm-fingerprint-by-newsboxx.webp\" class=\"float-left\" width=\"380\" alt=\"qualcomm-fingerprint-by-newsboxx\">\r\nThe organization is taking a major jump here, The new 2nd  Gen model estimates 8mm x 8mm, contrasted with the 4mm x 9mm surface region of the first-generation model, for 77 percent more surface zone. The new sensor is the <b><i>3rd under-display ultrasonic fingerprint sensor from Qualcomm</i></b>.\r\n<br>\r\nQualcomm guarantees that filtering a unique mark to unlock a smartphone will go 50% faster with the 3D Sonic 2nd Gen Sensor, ideally shutting the presentation hole to optical sensors which for the most part have demonstrated to in any case be prevalent as far as speed.\r\n<img src=\"img/home/fingerprint-sensor-by-qualcomm.webp\" class=\"float-right\" width=\"380\" alt=\"fingerprint-sensor-by-qualcomm\"><br><br>\r\nQualcomm said that the phone comes with a new 3D Sonic second Gen Sensor to be available from mid-2021. Qualcomm has quite been creating ultrasonic sensors for almost six years now. The sensors arrive at a large number of buyers through <b><i>Samsung</i></b>. A few blemishes in the innovation additionally surfaced at first, and a large portion of them was fixed through software updates.\r\n', 'Technology', 'Qualcomm Launch New 3D Sonic 2nd Gen Fingerprint Sensor, Samsung, Samsung\'s Galaxy S10 and S20, ultrasonic fingerprint sensor, ', '2021-01-12', '2021-01-12 16:42:23', 'Paresh', 44),
('2f8856a2-4cd0-11', 'vivo Y 20 A (800 x 460) (1).webp', 'Vivo Y20 A', 'Vivo Y20 A', 'VIVO Y20A arrived in INDIA with the triple rear camera at a medium range price', 'vivo-y20a-arrived-in-india-with-the-triple-rear-camera-at-medium-range-price', 'As we know the <b>VIVO mobile</b> has an <b>awesome camera</b> so these smartphones will also have awesome camera performance with the triple rear camera and also at just a cheap price it\'s base variant carries a price tag of just Rs 11,490 it might be a <b>good mobile at this price</b>.\r\n\r\n<b>VIVO Y20A launched</b> in two colors, Now this smartphone is on sale on its online store, VIVO Y20A has a Powerful battery with 5,000mAh that also supports the reverse charging <b>VIVO Y20A is live on the sale</b> on the online store, this smartphone was further launched a few weeks ago and it\'s live on sale today.\r\n\r\nIt comes with the waterdrop style notch display and <b>triple rear cameras</b> with 13mp+2mp+2mp, It had a wide display with 6.51-inch, It has a front camera with 8mp, It base Variant with 3 GB RAM 64GB it can be expanded up to 12GB it comes with OS Andriod 11, It has a screen resolution of 720 x 1600 pixels.\r\n\r\nIt comes with dual sim support with a dedicated microSD card slot, It supports 4G, GPS/A-Gps, FM radio, Micro-USB, and 3.5mm headphone jack it has a side-mounted fingerprint sensor. It supports the charging of 10W fast charging, the weight of the device 192 grams.', 'Mobile News', 'Vivo Y20 A', '2021-01-02', '2021-01-02 07:58:14', 'Pritesh', 96),
('50fc9f7b-5413-11', 'hootsuite-logo-by-newsboxx.webp', 'hootsuite-logo-by-newsboxx', 'hootsuite-logo-by-newsboxx', 'Social Media Marketing Using Hootsuite', 'social-media-marketing-using-hootsuite', 'If you are looking for the top <b><i>social networking sites</i></b> on the internet, Then look no further. just google it and you will get the results. I will provide you with the link below to get the full list of the top social networking sites and their user count. There is also a short description of each site in my signature. \r\n<h3 align=\"center\">What Is Hootsuite?</h3>\r\n<b><i>Hootsuite</i></b> is currently the second most popular <b><i>social media management tool</i></b> behind Twitter and has recently released its new version, Hootsuite Pro. if you want the stats just scroll down to the bottom of this article. First, you will discover the top <b>social networking sites</b> listed followed by the top 10 social media accounts.\r\n<img src=\"img/home/Hootsuite-dashboard-by-newsboxx.webp\" class=\"float-left\" width=\"380\" alt=\"Hootsuite-dashboard-by-newsboxx\">\r\nThen you will see all of the users that have created Hootsuite account, which a very powerful analytics tool that provides detailed information about how many people visit your site how active your users, what are pages they visit the most, where your visitors go after living your site and many some there is only a small list of applications.\r\n\r\n<h3 align=\"center\">Can Hootsuite Is Secure?</h3>\r\n<img src=\"img/home/hootsuite-by-newsboxx .webp\" class=\"float-center\" width=\"320\" alt=\"hootsuite-by-newsboxx\">\r\nHootsuite has integrated several highly advanced security features that can help to ensure the integrity and efficiency of your social media marketing efforts. vulnerability assessment system out only identifies potential hacking threats, But also provides a complete insight into the various types of attacks that are begin used to gain access to your network. Vulnerability assessment is a crucial component of a robust social media security plan. with highly customizable reporting capabilities and an intuitive, interface Hootsuite security complete. With paigle users are presented with a list of vulnerable profiles that need to be examined. \r\n\r\nDepending on the severity of the yet, villain the list of unlevel profiles can be narrowed down and users are then provided with a list of vulnerable profiles Hootsuite users can then manage multiple social networking profiles under a single login, preventing employees from accessing each profile individually. Manage Multiple Profiles: One of the most useful aspects of Hootsuite is its ability to manage multiple user profiles from a single platform.\r\n\r\nThat Hootsuite offers, but I hope that it gives you good rating points to explore the world of <b><i>social media marketing</i></b>. one cool aspect of Hootsuite pro is that it integrates with <b>Twitter</b> and <b>Facebook</b>. this makes it possible to manage your social media account from your smartphone or tablet. the developers of this amazing tool have seen everything and created the ultimate tool for anyone that wants to stay ahead of the competition.\r\n\r\n<h3 align=\"center\">Social Media Marketing Using Hootsuite</h3>\r\n<img src=\"img/home/social-media-marketing-by-newsboxx.webp\" class=\"float-right\" width=\"380\" alt=\"social-media-marketing-by-newsboxx\">\r\nusers can easily manage their <b>personal profiles</b>, Contact the various groups that they belong to, <b><i>send a message, post, comments, create links, and view polls</i></b>. If you use <b>Hootsuite</b> for managing several social accounts, you can also perform these functions from within your Hootsuite dashboard. The dashboard includes a link to your Hootsuite Free account, Where you can perform the majority of your vulnerability assessment tasks. This means that instead of having to open up each application to see what you are doing, You can perform all of your vulnerability assessment tasks from within your Hootsuite Free Account dashboard.\r\n', 'Social Media', 'Social Media Marketing Using Hootsuite, what is Hootsuite,Can Hootsuite Is Secure?, Facebook, Twitter, Instagram...', '2021-01-11', '2021-01-11 13:45:46', 'Paresh', 47),
('549a070e-50c4-11', 'whats-app-by-newsboxx.webp', 'Privacy Policy of WhatsApp', 'Privacy Policy of WhatsApp', 'What is the New Privacy Policy of WhatsApp?', 'Privacy-Policy-of-WhatsApp-changed', 'As <b>WhatsApp is one of the Most Used Apps in INDIA</b>, Nearby every person uses WhatsApp for communication purposes but now a day WhatsApp is planning to launch an online market or store on WhatsApp due to these they are willing to make changes in their Privacy Policy.\r\n\r\nNow <b>WhatsApp</b> will remain encrypted end to end, which means that messages will be safe between the users, Now as <b>Facebook has owned WhatsApp</b>, they will host some new services in WhatsApp such as stores and manage their WhatsApp chats, and also there will be more integration of Facebook in these matters, Now WhatsApp will collect the data such as battery level, signal strength, app version, browser information, mobile network, connection information, mobiles numbers, mobile operator or ISP, language time zone, IP address, device operations information, this <b>WhatsApp Policy</b> was not first undertaken but now it will be undertaken.\r\n\r\nALL our data such as <b>mobile numbers, IP address, mac address, Smartphone device</b> information will be shared on Facebook these means that our data will become public, Now in the update there will be no banner ads that disturb us while performing our works there will no pop-ups ads, WhatsApp new Policy told that even if we have not used GPS then also they will have our details such as IP address and other information like phone number area codes to estimate general location, We would have to accept this <b>Privacy Policy</b> till February 8, 2021, if we did not accept these Policy our account will be banned, So we have to accept there Policy.', 'Social Media', 'WhatsApp New Privacy Policy\'s', '2021-01-07', '2021-01-07 08:42:50', 'Pritesh', 589),
('7758dc25-4c31-11', 'jio_offers_free_calling.webp', 'jio_offers_free_calling', 'jio_offers_free_calling', 'JIO offer Free Calling for Jio to non-jio Networks', 'jio-offer-free-calling-for-jio-to-non-jio-networks', 'JIO had planned that they had removed the complimentary data which was seen in the list of top up plans on their official website. JIO on their official site had announced that for every Rs10 spent on off-net voice call you will be getting complimentary 1GB Data for free.\r\n\r\nMain highlights are such as <b>JIO</b> on Thursday noted on TRAI Bill and kept regime that being implemented in INDIA from January 1, 2021, On Occasion of <b>New Year</b>, as per that ending IUC charges for all domestic voice calls, That means all the domestic calls will be Free, Also JIO has noted that the charges for the customers will be exactly equivalent to applicable IUC charges, Now all the domestic calls made from <b>JIO network</b> to Non-JIO network will be <b>totally Free</b> no special charges will be needed, JIO had announced that they had removed its complementary data vouchers it gave with off-net calling plans.\r\n\r\nJIO on its website had noted that for every Rs10 spent on off-net mobile voice calls, An additional complimentary 1GB Data will be credited to the consumer without any Cost, Now JIO had scrapped off additional data it was given as compensation to inter-connected usage charge for all call such as JIO to non-JIO calls. All the top-up plans will be now offered only <b>Talktime plans</b>. Development was first noted by the only tech.', 'Telecome', 'Jio to non jio calls free', '2021-01-01', '2021-01-01 13:01:30', 'Paresh', 46),
('90639d84-4cc3-11', 'tesla_800x388.webp', 'tesla coming in india', 'tesla coming in india', 'TESLA ARRIVAL IN INDIA IS CONFIRMED BY MR\'S NITIN GADKARI', 'tesla-arrival-in-india-is-confirmed-by-mrs-nitin-gadkari', 'Mr. Gadkari had said that Tesla will be starting its first operation with sales and then they may be looking to assemble TESLA in INDIA for manufacturing based on the response to their cars. In October <b>TESLA CEO ELON MUSK TWEETED</b> that company will be coming to INDIA in 2021.\r\n\r\nThe <b>UNION MINISTER FOR ROAD TRANSPORT AND HIGHWAYS AND THE MINISTER OF MICRO</b>, small and medium enterprises <b>Mr. NITIN GADKARI</b> on the following Monday told clean energy and electric vehicle top most company the TESLA will be starting its operation in <b>INDIA</b> in early 2021, the Government had also suggested the other electrical vehicle manufacturing company that they should also try to make the vehicles as advanced as TESLA and also affordable, AS per these INDIA is going to be THE NUMBER 1 MANUFACTURING HUB FOR AUTOMOBILES <b>ELON MUSK the CEO of TESLA</b> had checked with the ministry about the company progress in India.\r\n\r\nAccording to the reports the first model to come in India will the affordable name of the first model launching in INDIA will be <b>TESLA MODEL 3</b>, Booking may be starting in few weeks, The sale may be staring in the Second half of the year, THE TESLA MODEL 3 PRICE IN INDIA will be Rs 55 Lakhs onwards, As the TESLA ELECTRIC CARS are most awaited cars in INDIA, Along with the cars <b>TESLA SUPERCHARGERS</b> are also famous for its speedy charging, The price TESLA SUPERCHARGER price may be 850Rs for full charging of vehicle, TESLA MODEL S PRICE IN INDIA WILL BE RS 1.50cr*, <b>TESLA MODEL X PRICE IN INDIA</b> MAY BE RS 2.00cr*, AS these cars, are in huge demand. TESLA had expected to launch its 5 cars in 2021-2022. TESLA will also help INDIA in building up its economy as due to this pandemic the economy of the INDIA got fluctuate.\r\n', 'Electric Vehicle', 'Tesla in India', '2021-01-02', '2021-01-02 06:27:18', 'Paresh', 73),
('b78fbe8b-49f2-11', 'mini_rog phone 3.webp', 'Asus Rog SmartPhone ', 'Asus Rog SmartPhone ', 'Grab Asus ROG in Lowest Price', 'Grab-Asus-ROG-in-lowest-price', 'Now Asus Rog is available at the lowest price on Flipkart, you can get the best deals on Rog during the Flipkart year-end sale that has started today. As the Asus Rog is the Best Gaming Smartphone of the year 2020, you can grab the best Gaming Smartphone for just Rs 44,999 for the base variant. As the price of these base variant prices normally was Rs46,999, so you get Rs2000 Discount on the Smartphone, As per the offer the top variant of the Asus Rog 3 is also up with Rs2000 discount in the sale.\r\n\r\nyou can also get an extra Rs1000 off if you have <b>ICCI Bank Credit Card</b>, you can get an <b>extra discount</b> of Rs1000 on both variants of <b>Asus Rog 3</b>. It means you can grab the Asus Rog Phone (8GB RAM & 128GB storage) at its lowest price which is just Rs 43,999 while the top variant that is (12GB RAM & 128GB storage) variant in just Rs 46,999.\r\n\r\nThese prices make this Smartphone the <b>best flagship Smartphone of the year</b>, As it has the best processor which is <b>Qualcomm snapdragon 865+ processor</b> it is the <b>best 5G Processor</b> also it has the top quality hardware makes the phone very fast so you can enjoy all your gaming very easily. the processor speed can be upgraded to the max performance, you can enjoy the games with highest graphics setting, These Smartphone have all the quality which makes it the best gaming phone, camera of Asus ROG Phone 3 are also quite good it has 64 MP camera with the Sony sensors which are best sensors which are used in many flagship phones.\r\n\r\nThe battery backup of the phone is impressive which is a <b>6000 mAh battery</b> that powers the phone the weight of the phone is also light which is about 240 grams, The battery is long-lasting which can be used throughout the day.', 'Mobile News', 'Asus_Rog_On_Sale', '2020-12-29', '2020-12-29 16:27:16', 'Paresh', 181),
('bd5fc852-42af-11', 'pubg-mobile-image-by-newsboxx.webp', 'PUBG_MOBILE_PUBG_IMG', 'PUBG_MOBILE_PUBG_IMG', 'PUBG Mobile: Here is The List of Countries Where PUBG Was Banned This Year ', 'pubg-mobile-here-is-the-list-of-countries-where-pubg-was-banned-this-year', 'PUBG Mobile has not had a smooth ride this year. From the mid of 2020 PUBG Mobile has faced a very tough time. On 1st July Pakistan Telecommunication Authority (PTA) decided to ban the game. They say that people are completing against PUBG. Also, they stated that children are facing physical and <b>psychological health issues</b> due to their addiction to the game.\r\n\r\nAfter that, on the 2nd September <b>Indian Ministry of Electronics and Information Technology</b> announced that <b>India banned some Chinese apps</b> due to security concerns, The Ministry says that <b>PUBG Mobile and 118 other Chinese apps are stealing user\'s data in an authorized manner</b>. Hence the banned as announced.\r\n\r\nAfter <b>India and Pakistan, Afghanistan</b> is the latest country that announced a ban against PUBG Mobile on Thursday. The Afghanistan Telecommunication Regulatory Authority (ATRA) announces a temporary ban on the game due to social and security concerns.\r\n\r\nThe Major reasons behind these bans are the addictiveness of the game and security concerns after the whole banned happens <b>PUBG Mobile</b> Tring to Stop their Partnership with Tencent and they try to find a new investor to start their services in these countries. Because approximately 33 to 50 million users are from these countries. These can create huge <b>Financial impact</b> on a company.\r\n\r\n<button><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tencent.iglite&hl=en_IN&gl=US\">PUBG MOBILE LITE</a></button>\r\n\r\n<button><a href=\"https://www.pubgmobile.in/\">PUBG MOBILE INDIA WEBSITE </a></button>\r\n\r\n\r\n		\r\n', 'Esports', 'PUBG MOBILE BANS IN INDIA, PAKISTAN AND IN AFGHANISTAN', '2020-12-19', '2020-12-21 13:32:00', 'Paresh', 340),
